fields.slidedescrb1: Discover, Present, Analyze Real-Time Data from Worldwide Sources

fields.question: Do you retrieve data from password-protected cameras?
fields.answer: Only if the camera owner gives us the password. We will not guess the password of any camera.

fields.question: Are you recording all data continuously?
What do the cameras see?
fields.answer: Most cameras observe traffic or outdoor scenes.

fields.question: Will you send me any email?
fields.answer: We intend to keep the email traffic low.

fields.question: If I register, what do you do my data (such as my email address)?
What do you do with the data? Are you tracking where I go?
fields.answer: We do not intend to indentify any individual. Thus, we do not know where you are.

fields.question: I have cameras. Can I add my cameras to your site?
fields.answer: Not yet. We will add that feature soon.

fields.question: What is the frame rate?
fields.answer: The frame rates, as well as the resolutions, vary based on the cameras.

fields.question: Where do you get the data?
fields.answer: Universities, governments, and some other web sites.
